note bottom of App
Implemented interaction flow is extensive (selection, drag,
reconnect, preview edges, delete, shortcuts).
Important caveat: routeAllEdges() contains a fallback polyline
router because ScopeCanvasRouting::EdgeRouter::routeAll()
currently returns empty.
end note

@enduml
